{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/current-events-christmas/christmas-events","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Christmas events","meta_description":"Christmas events and Covid-19","content":{"processed":"<h2><strong>Recommendations</strong></h2>\n<p>Christmas is associated not only with <strong>Christmas dinner</strong> but also with a large number of social and cultural events throughout December. At present, there are <strong>no measures governing</strong> the Christmas market regime. In some cities, however, it is already known that Christmas <strong>markets will not take place</strong> in the usual form.</p>\n<p><strong>The lighting of Christmas trees</strong> is most often an event organized by the municipality. You can find out more information from the website of the municipality, local radio, etc.</p>\n<p>If <strong>masses</strong> are allowed, follow the basic hygienic principles (principle Wear Z – face masks, social distance, disinfect your hands).</p>\n<p>It is not yet known what measures will apply in the period of December concerning <strong>the</strong> <strong>Christmas parties</strong> (corporate, etc.).<br />\n </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/current-events-christmas/christmas-events"},"changed":"2020-11-22T17:06:47+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-04T22:49:22+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"emoji_people"},"situation_type":{"name":"CURRENT EVENTS: Christmas","path":{"alias":"/situations/current-events-christmas"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"calendar_today"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":" Shopping malls","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/shopping-malls","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Markets, farmers markets","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/markets-farmers-markets","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"las